Hosts extension (os-hosts)
==========================

Administrators only, depending on policy settings.

Lists, shows hosts.


List all hosts for a project
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. rest_method::  GET /v3/{admin_project_id}/os-hosts

Lists all hosts summary info that is not disabled.

