--------------

.. rest_status_code:: success ../status.yaml

   - 200

.. rest_status_code:: error ../status.yaml

   - 400
   - 401
   - 403

Request
-------

.. rest_parameters:: parameters.yaml

   - admin_project_id: admin_project_id


